name: Running Makeup
description:
The LoRA to use if you want a girl to look messy after a good cry, or after a good experience deep throat.

Needs adjustment and probably levels of running, but generally delivers well, especially with the Uberrealistic Dreamy PFG and Pyros BJ model which i used for the examples. Some models will result in garbled images, this can sometimes be fixed by adjusting the LoRA's priority from 1 to 0.6-0.8.

It doesn't work with anime, but might work with stylized stuff.
